{
  "stem": "27759.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] panels that they would raise and lower.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, it-- it was screened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When it was hot, you just raised it during the day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if it was a cool night, you'd lower it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I think they slept six to a barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then we encountered some difficulties with the white civilians and the white soldiers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was name-calling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and then there were fights that broke out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they would call us niggers and blackie and all sorts of--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Blackies.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nigger.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all sorts of name-calling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And spit at us and so forth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "White soldiers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, the soldiers weren't integrated then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had all-black outfits and a white outfit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we have a colonel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name was Colonel Castle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a battalion commander.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a white man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he treated us-- he was a good man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so-- because Colonel Castle, he was the one that was responsible to have our outfit transferred out of Camp Shelby, Mississippi, because he told Washington, DC-- the high command in Washington-- told them if they didn't ship us out of there, he would not be held responsible for what would happen.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was going to arm the battalion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was going to arm us-- arm the battalion and let them go up against these white soldiers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was only there three weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they shipped us to Camp Forrest, Tennessee.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's where I completed my basic training, at Camp Forrest, Tennessee.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And how was the treatment to you as being black American there?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At Camp Forrest?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was somewhat similar, but it wasn't as bad as it was in Mississippi.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- you encountered a lot of prejudice in the South-- well, at Tennessee, Alabama, Georgia.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
